          "whatWentWrong": "He accidentally misspelled 'their' as 'thdir'."
        },
        {
          "questionRef": "[27]",
          "type": "oeq",
          "whatWentWrong": "He made a quick copying slip, writing 'dramed' instead of 'framed'."
        }
      ],
      "strategic_advice": "After writing your answer, do a quick check: does the word start a new sentence? If so, it needs a **capital letter**. Also, read your written word backwards letter by letter to catch small spelling slips.",
      "trigger_keywords": [
        "fill in each blank",
